HEADWORD: Forceful
<hw>Force"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of or
processing force; exerting force; mighty.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Force"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

